PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?seat ?seatLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q7159 wdt:P159 ?seat .
  ?seat rdfs:label ?seatLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?seatLabel ) = "en" ) FILTER ( ?seat = wd:Q3624 )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?zipCode WHERE {
  ?partOfSeattle wdt:P131 wd:Q5083 .
  ?partOfSeattle wdt:P281 ?zipCode .
  FILTER ( REGEX( ?zipCode , "^[0-9]{5}$" ) )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?placeOfBirth ?educationalInstitution WHERE {
  wd:Q1744 wdt:P19 ?placeOfBirth .
  wd:Q1744 wdt:P69 ?educationalInstitution .
  FILTER ( ?educationalInstitution = wd:Q7353940 )
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?actor WHERE {
  wd:Q3577037 p:P161 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P161 ?actor .

}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?name ?dateOfBirth ?placeOfBirth ?countryOfCitizenship WHERE {
  wd:Q133622 rdfs:label ?name .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?name ) = "en" ) wd:Q133622 wdt:P569 ?dateOfBirth .
  wd:Q133622 wdt:P19 ?placeOfBirth .
  wd:Q133622 wdt:P27 ?countryOfCitizenship .
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?vicePresident WHERE {
  ?vicePresident wdt:P39 wd:Q11699 .
  ?vicePresident wdt:P580 ?start .
  ?vicePresident wdt:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= '2001-01-20T00:00:00Z' ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?end >= '1993-01-20T00:00:00Z' ^^ xsd:dateTime )
}

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?actor WHERE {
  wd:Q4169030 p:P175 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P175 ?actor .

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT ?start ?end WHERE {
  wd:Q91 p:P39 [ ps:P39 wd:Q11696 ; pq:P580 ?start ; pq:P582 ?end ] .
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT ?team ?joinDate WHERE {
  wd:Q169452 p:P54 ?teamStatement .
  ?teamStatement ps:P54 ?team .
  ?teamStatement pq:P580 ?joinDate .
  FILTER ( ?team != wd:Q6460027 )
}
ORDER BY ASC ( ?joinDate )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?cup ?year WHERE {
  ?cup wdt:P31 wd:Q1144743 .
  ?cup wdt:P585 ?year .
  ?cup wdt:P1346 wd:Q203008 .
  FILTER ( ?year > "2010" ^^ xsd:dateTime )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?year )
LIMIT 10

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?state ?coordinates WHERE {
  wd:Q1319988 wdt:P131 ?county .
  ?county wdt:P131 ?state .
  wd:Q1319988 wdt:P625 ?coordinates .
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?religion ( COUNT( ?person ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?person wdt:P140 ?religion .
  ?person wdt:P27 wd:Q801 .
}
GROUP BY ?religion
ORDER BY DESC ( ?count )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?vicePresident WHERE {
  ?vicePresident wdt:P39 wd:Q11699 .
  ?vicePresident p:P39 ?positionStatement .
  ?positionStatement pq:P580 ?start .
  ?positionStatement pq:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= "1963-11-22" ^^ xsd:date && ?end >= "1961-01-20" ^^ xsd:date ) .
  FILTER ( ?vicePresident = wd:Q9640 )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>

ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q296403 p:P54 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P54 ?team .
  ?statement pq:P585 ?time .
  FILTER ( ?time > "2020-01-01T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?primeMinister ?primeMinisterLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q29 p:P6 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P6 ?primeMinister ; pq:P580 ?startDate ; pq:P582 ?endDate .
  FILTER ( ?startDate <= "2011-12-31" ^^ xsd:date && ?endDate >= "2011-01-01" ^^ xsd:date ) OPTIONAL {
    ?primeMinister rdfs:label ?primeMinisterLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?primeMinisterLabel ) = "en" )
  }
  FILTER ( BOUND( ?primeMinisterLabel ) )
}

  wd:Q5680 wdt:P17 ?country .
  wd:Q5680 wdt:P131 ?mosul .
  wd:Q5680 wdt:P625 ?coordinates .
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?governor ?governorLabel ?startDate ?endDate WHERE {
  wd:Q69319 p:P39 ?positionStatement .
  ?positionStatement ps:P39 wd:Q17989863 ; pq:P580 ?startDate ; pq:P582 ?endDate .
  FILTER ( ?startDate <= "2011-12-31" ^^ xsd:date ) FILTER ( ?endDate >= "2011-01-01" ^^ xsd:date ) BIND( wd:Q69319 AS ?governor ) OPTIONAL {
    wd:Q69319 rdfs:label ?governorLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?governorLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}
